{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"1a35025f-008c-52ad-86a3-46782abce7fe","excerpt":"Being in control is the best aspect of using PDF as a read it later service: you can modify how the website looks like, save it so that it’s yours to read, annotate and store however you like to.  It’s not perfect, but it’s surprisingly good. styling…","frontmatter":{"date":"July 25, 2020","type":null,"path":"/writings/pdf-as-a-read-it-later-service","title":"PDF as a Read It Later Service","tags":["research"],"summary":"PDF seems to be the best format to read books on iPad, and now I've started using it for reading web long reads as well. Being in control is the best part: You can decide how the website looks like, save it so it's yours to read and annotate however you like, and store it forever.","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.0161290322580645,"src":"/static/ad20bac7e8d853099b731d0c5d123d8c/8f7df/pdf-longread-annotation.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ad20bac7e8d853099b731d0c5d123d8c/e7079/pdf-longread-annotation.jpg 63w,\n/static/ad20bac7e8d853099b731d0c5d123d8c/1ada3/pdf-longread-annotation.jpg 125w,\n/static/ad20bac7e8d853099b731d0c5d123d8c/8f7df/pdf-longread-annotation.jpg 250w,\n/static/ad20bac7e8d853099b731d0c5d123d8c/01f8d/pdf-longread-annotation.jpg 375w,\n/static/ad20bac7e8d853099b731d0c5d123d8c/0f3a1/pdf-longread-annotation.jpg 500w,\n/static/ad20bac7e8d853099b731d0c5d123d8c/4dd6d/pdf-longread-annotation.jpg 1668w","sizes":"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px"}}}},"fields":{"slug":"/information-overload/pdf-as-a-read-it-later-service/","readingTime":{"text":"9 min read"}}}},{"node":{"id":"e607bdc5-53ce-5e78-800d-c096d9228acd","excerpt":"What is the best feed aggregator, reader or feed service depends on your needs, so this is highly opinionated towards my personal needs - your's will vary so take this writing as a personal journey instead of an objective comparison.  As I wrote, I…","frontmatter":{"dat